  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have awoken, trapped in a strange house.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The fire is all but dead and the wind is howling outside. There are strange artefacts around the house and you soon come to realise that this is no ordinary house. This charmingly creepy little cottage appears to be the home of a witch!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must escape by finding, using and combining various items, which can be found around the several areas of the house.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323120/extras/6aabb83a05b3d108dc343a630a38f2eb.avif?t=1771927004\" width=589 height=314 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore, discover secrets, try your hand at magic, unlock  spells and get out of the house before the witch Grimazel returns!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323120/extras/9cbf7be5eb3f57311664f307ac21b1e1.avif?t=1771927004\" width=281 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Escape from Grimazel's Cottage</strong> is a point and click, first person escape/adventure game of magic and witchcraft.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323120/extras/3d6778daccf093f789a127cea193aacc.avif?t=1771927004\" width=476 height=290 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >​<strong>​</strong>Explore an eerie cottage, discovering and crafting items to aid you through several hand-drawn rooms of the house.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A traditional point and click interface designed to make exploring, using, combing and creating items a breeze - leaving you to ponder what your next move might be!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft magic wands using secret recipes hidden in ancient books and forgotten pages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn 8 different magic spells and uncover age-old secrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the darkest corners and the highest shelves, and uncover the wonders of magic in order to find a way to escape this witch's cottage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323120/extras/63159b5d4a29f3dd1745420f2767fb18.avif?t=1771927004\" width=616 height=412 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have awoken, trapped in a strange house.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The fire is all but dead and the wind is howling outside. There are strange artefacts around the house and you soon come to realise that this is no ordinary house. This charmingly creepy little cottage appears to be the home of a witch!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must escape by finding, using and combining various items, which can be found around the several areas of the house.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323120/extras/6aabb83a05b3d108dc343a630a38f2eb.avif?t=1771927004\" width=589 height=314 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore, discover secrets, try your hand at magic, unlock  spells and get out of the house before the witch Grimazel returns!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323120/extras/9cbf7be5eb3f57311664f307ac21b1e1.avif?t=1771927004\" width=281 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Escape from Grimazel's Cottage</strong> is a point and click, first person escape/adventure game of magic and witchcraft.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323120/extras/3d6778daccf093f789a127cea193aacc.avif?t=1771927004\" width=476 height=290 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >​<strong>​</strong>Explore an eerie cottage, discovering and crafting items to aid you through several hand-drawn rooms of the house.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A traditional point and click interface designed to make exploring, using, combing and creating items a breeze - leaving you to ponder what your next move might be!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft magic wands using secret recipes hidden in ancient books and forgotten pages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn 8 different magic spells and uncover age-old secrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the darkest corners and the highest shelves, and uncover the wonders of magic in order to find a way to escape this witch's cottage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323120/extras/63159b5d4a29f3dd1745420f2767fb18.avif?t=1771927004\" width=616 height=412 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
